doomsday is a 1928 american romance drama silent film directed by rowland v. lee and starring florence vidor and gary cooper . written by julian johnson , donald w. lee , and doris anderson , based on the 1927 novel doomsday by warwick &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , the film is about a woman who marries a wealthy landowner to escape her life of poverty , leaving behind the handsome farmer she truly loves . produced by jesse l. lasky , rowland v. lee , hector turnbull , and adolph zukor for paramount pictures , doomsday was released on february 18 , 1928 in the united states .